Class Deadline

  • java.lang.Object
    • negotiator.Deadline

  • public class Deadline
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains the deadline - either rounds based or time based.

    Deadline is a final object and can be serialized to xml.

    Author:
    W.Pasman
